title: Kansas City Confidential ( Film Noir, 1952) John Payne, Lee Van Cleef Colorized Movie, Subtitles

sources.title: Kansas City Confidential ( Film Noir, 1952) John Payne, Lee Van Cleef Colorized Movie, Subtitles
sources.description: A down-on-his-luck ex-GI finds himself framed for an armored car robbery. When he’s finally released for lack of evidence–after having been beaten up and tortured by the police–he sets out to discover who set him up, and why. The trail leads him into Mexico and a web of hired killers and corrupt cops.
